    splashSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8101c6bac3c7ca0479f1944cd9245658, type: 3}
    shortLore: Alex Reynolds, known as Slugger, was a rising star in baseball celebrated
      for his powerful batting. During a crucial game under a starlit sky, stardust
      infused him with superhuman strength and agility. Now wielding a stardust-charged
      bat, Slugger defends humanity from Underworld threats with resilience and heroism.
    baseHp: 100
    baseAttack: 200
    baseDefense: 200
    baseSpecial: 100
  - sourceNumericId: 2
    id: ace
    displayName: Ace
    pseudo: Ace
    fullName: Sarah Thompson
    description: Sarah Thompson, also known as Ace, was a celebrated professional
      baseball player known for her powerful batting and strategic leadership. Exposure
      to stardust enhanced her abilities, granting superhuman strength and agility.
      Embracing her new powers, Ace wields a stardust-charged baseball bat against
      Underworld threats, driven by her passion for sportsmanship and determination
      to protect humanity.
    rarityDefinition: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e8933f5e086d9c40b20fb0c41335fe6, type: 2}
    typeDefinition: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4554b0ab2c8a29a44bf787114745010f, type: 2}
